<!doctype html>
<html>
  <head>
    <link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
    <link href="./styles/styles.css" rel="stylesheet">
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- BEGIN BLOG HEADER -->
    <div class="section-blog-header">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 col-sm-12">
            <h1 style="color:white">Empresa: <%= @offer.enterprise.name %></h1>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- END BLOG HEADER -->

    <!-- BEGIN BLOG POST -->
    <div class="section-blog-post">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-12">
            <div class="post-container">

              <h1>INFORMAÇÕES SOBRE A OFERTA:</h1>


              <div class="featured-image">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1456394555490-ef1bf0aedc46?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&s=828f8fc43a22dc389009b817ba49bae0&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1050&q=80" width="100%">
              </div>

              <div class="post-body">
                <p>Resumo: <%= @offer.enterprise.abstract %></p>

                <% @offer.enterprise.founders.each do |founder| %>
                  <ul>
                    <li><%= founder.name  %></li>
                  </ul>
                <% end %>

                <p>Descrição da oferta pública: <%= @offer.description %></p>

                <ul>
                    <li>Valor Unitário: <%= @offer.pu %></li>
                    <li>Percentual<%= @offer.share %>%</li>
                    <li>Quantidade: <%= @offer.units %></li>
                </ul>
                <p>Observação: Antes de completar seu investimento mantenha atualizados todos os seus dados cadastrais(nome completo, CPF, endereço, e endereço eletrônico). Caso o seu cadastro não esteja completo você será automaticamente direcionado para a página do cadastro ao solicitar um investimento.</p>
                <div class="thermo">
                  <%= render "thermomether" %>
                </div>
              </div>



                <div class="banner-content" style="display: flex; justify-content: center;" >
                  <% if current_user.name != nil && current_user.address != nil && current_user.cpf != nil%>
                    <%= link_to 'Investir', new_offer_investment_path(@offer), {:style=>"background-color: red; width: 250px;", :class => "btn btn-primary btn-lg"} %>
                  <% else %>
                    <%= link_to 'Investir', "/users/edit", {:style=>"background-color: red; width: 250px;", :class => "btn btn-primary btn-lg"} %>
                  <% end %>
                </div>



              <div id="disqus_thread"></div>
              <script>

              /**
              *  RECOMMENDED CONFIGURATION VARIABLES: EDIT AND UNCOMMENT THE SECTION BELOW TO INSERT DYNAMIC VALUES FROM YOUR PLATFORM OR CMS.
              *  LEARN WHY DEFINING THESE VARIABLES IS IMPORTANT: https://disqus.com/admin/universalcode/#configuration-variables*/
              /*
              var disqus_config = function () {
              this.page.url = PAGE_URL;  // Replace PAGE_URL with your page's canonical URL variable
              this.page.identifier = PAGE_IDENTIFIER; // Replace PAGE_IDENTIFIER with your page's unique identifier variable
              };
              */
              (function() { // DON'T EDIT BELOW THIS LINE
              var d = document, s = d.createElement('script');
              s.src = 'https://convexit-yc-apital.disqus.com/embed.js';
              s.setAttribute('data-timestamp', +new Date());
              (d.head || d.body).appendChild(s);
              })();
              </script>
              <noscript>Please enable JavaScript to view the <a href="https://disqus.com/?ref_noscript">comments powered by Disqus.</a></noscript>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
